555
00:45:17,200 --> 00:45:18,804
To the best of your recollection,

556
00:45:18,960 --> 00:45:21,804
what were the last words
the missing person spoke to you?

557
00:45:27,400 --> 00:45:29,050
I don't remember.

558
00:45:29,240 --> 00:45:30,969
You don't remember?

559
00:45:32,160 --> 00:45:33,321
No.

560
00:45:40,360 --> 00:45:42,124
To the best of your knowledge,
did the missing person

561
00:45:42,280 --> 00:45:45,170
ever express a desire
to hurt him or herself? If so, why?

562
00:45:45,320 --> 00:45:46,890
Absolutely not.

563
00:45:47,040 --> 00:45:49,805
Have you ever expressed
a desire to hurt yourself? If so, why?

564
00:45:49,960 --> 00:45:51,041
No.

565
00:45:52,040 --> 00:45:53,929
To the best of your knowledge,
did the missing person

566
00:45:54,080 --> 00:45:56,082
withdraw more than $1,000
