00:53:08,960 --> 00:53:10,485
Mary's asleep.

653
00:53:10,640 --> 00:53:12,005
Jill's putting the baby down upstairs.

654
00:53:12,160 --> 00:53:13,764
Okay, I'll go up and help out.

655
00:53:13,960 --> 00:53:15,371
We need to talk.

656
00:53:18,280 --> 00:53:20,282
Can we do this tomorrow?

657
00:53:21,320 --> 00:53:22,606
It's important.

658
00:53:24,120 --> 00:53:28,648
Yes, honey, I know it's important,
but can we just--

659
00:53:28,800 --> 00:53:31,041
I need to talk to you now, Nora.

660
00:53:41,160 --> 00:53:44,084
Have you been noticing that I've been

