662
00:53:48,800 --> 00:53:49,961
What?

663
00:53:53,320 --> 00:53:55,004
I'm letting you handcuff me
to the bed every night,

664
00:53:55,160 --> 00:53:57,811
and we're acting like
that's totally normal.

665
00:54:00,400 --> 00:54:06,009
I left the baby... I forgot the baby,
and you act like that's no big deal.

666
00:54:06,680 --> 00:54:09,889
- You had your hands full. it happens.
- I'm seeing someone.

667
00:54:12,320 --> 00:54:13,446
What?

668
00:54:14,400 --> 00:54:15,401
Um...

669
00:54:15,840 --> 00:54:19,049
I've been seeing someone.

670
00:54:23,760 --> 00:54:24,886
Who?

671
00:54:27,520 --> 00:54:28,851
Patti Levin.

672
00:54:31,920 --> 00:54:35,083
She ran the Guilty Remnant in Mapleton.

673
00:54:47,080 --> 00:54:48,605
But she's dead.

674
00:54:54,840 --> 00:54:57,810
It started happening
right after we found Lily,

675
00:54:59,200 --> 00:55:00,326
when you moved in.

676
00:55:01,920 --> 00:55:04,685
I thought she'd go away when we came here.

677
00:55:07,880 --> 00:55:09,291
She didn't.

678
00:55:16,120 --> 00:55:18,168
Are you seeing her right now?

679
00:55:21,400 --> 00:55:22,526
Yeah.

680
00:55:23,960 --> 00:55:25,803
<i>Is she talking to you?</i>

681
00:55:28,840 --> 00:55:29,921
Yeah.

682
00:55:33,880 --> 00:55:35,405
What's she saying?

683
00:55:37,160 --> 00:55:38,605
<i>She's saying...</i>

684
00:55:41,520 --> 00:55:44,649
<i>She's saying
